        <content><![CDATA[<h1 class="title topictitle1">Create a Finance Case</h1>
<div class="body taskbody">
<p class="shortdesc">This application allows the Finance department to manage tickets opened with them.</p>
<ol id="sys_report_template-normal__steps_ygl_2gd_z1b" class="ol steps"><li class="li step"><span class="ph cmd"> Use field &#34;Assigned To&#34; to assign the case to a finance user.<br /></span></li><li class="li step"><span class="ph cmd"><span class="ph uicontrol">Select the appropriate priority based on the nature of request</span>. Shorter or longer SLAs will be applied base on the case priority.<br /></span></li><li class="li step"><span class="ph cmd"><span class="ph uicontrol">Add work notes as necessary as you progress towards the resolution of the case.</span><br /></span></li><li class="li step"><span class="ph cmd"><span class="ph uicontrol">Once the case has been resolved, add closuse notes.</span></span></li><li class="li step"><span class="ph cmd"><span class="ph uicontrol">Finally, complete the ticket by changing the field &#34;State&#34; accordingly or by pressing the button &#34;Complete Case&#34;. </span></span></li></ol>
</div>
